News.headline: FA Youth Cup Second Round Draw
News.page_title: FA Youth Cup Second Round Draw
News.URL_keywords: FA Youth Cup Second Round Draw
News.short_description: The Daggers have been drawn to play Luton Town away in the second round of the FA Youth Cup.
News.description: After defeating Colchester United 7-3 at the Chigwell Construction Stadium on Wednesday, the Daggers will play Luton Town in the next round of the cup, the fixture is to be played by Saturday 19th November .
